No. 11-7270. Reginald Matheiw Castel, Petitioner v. Eric H. Holder, Jr., Attorney General. 565 U.S. 1148, 132 S. Ct. 1037,

181 L. Ed. 2d 791,

2012 U.S. LEXIS 470. January 9, 2012.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit denied.

Justice Kagan took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.

Same case below, 427 Fed. Appx. 103.
